ygData.msgSnippet: Where does the (I believe female dark elf?) SK with the Barbed Leggings spawn at in Befallen? I know it s level 3, but I don t know where. I Spent ALOT of time
ygData.messageBody:
Where does the (I believe female dark elf?) SK with the Barbed Leggings
spawn at in Befallen? I know it's level 3, but I don't know where. I Spent
ALOT of time in BF with another character, but never saw this SK (my groups
would never go looking for her though...somehting about "She took out my
entire group of 20s...blah blah blah"...well, I'm a 29th Shaman now, and
ready to kick some booty to get this...heh). Also, spawn frequency (rate 20
minute like Ogre SK or 30min-20hours like Troll SK with BBC?), and drop
frequency if you know it.
